      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are mistaken to believe that your absence would bring them peace; the guilt of losing you would become a heavier, more permanent burden than the stress you currently cause. True selflessness is not in disappearing, but in fighting for the very life that allows you to be there for them, even through the pain. Please consider that your children need you more than they need to breathe without you, and there are people who can help you carry this weight without ever having to leave.",
